---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About CollegeLacrosseSchedule.com"
  description="Learn how CollegeLacrosseSchedule.com aggregates game schedules, streaming links, and rankings for NCAA lacrosse."
  canonical="https://collegelacrosseschedule.com/about"
>
  <section class="rounded-xl bg-white p-6 shadow-card">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy">About</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-navy/80">
      CollegeLacrosseSchedule.com is a dedicated schedule and streaming hub for NCAA lacrosse fans. We aggregate verified
      broadcast information, rankings, and odds so you can quickly find where to watch each matchup.
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-sm text-navy/80">
      <li>Schedules are scraped every 12 hours with robots.txt compliance and fallback caching.</li>
      <li>Rankings are scraped every 24 hours from NCAA ranking sources.</li>
      <li>All outbound streaming links route through our watch tracking page before redirecting.</li>
      <li>Odds are provided for entertainment only where available.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>
